Liverpool new boy Mario Balotelli has taken to Instagram to thank his AC Milan team-mates and fans of the Serie A side for supporting him during his time at the club.

Balotelli, who sealed a £16million move to Liverpool on Monday, revealed his gratitude towards the club he represented since leaving Manchester City in January 2013.

The Italian striker stated on his arrival at Liverpool that he was pleased to have sealed a move back to the Premier League.

